Set and export a $CONFIG_PATH environment variable to point to this directory.

Symlink relevant config files to the home directory. For example:
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/gitconfig ~/.gitconfig
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/pythonrc ~/.pythonrc
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/vim ~/.vim
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/vimrc ~/.vimrc
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/zshrc ~/.zshrc
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/rspec ~/.rspec
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/inputrc ~/.inputrc
  ln -s $CONFIG_PATH/irbrc ~/.irbrc
